Informations:

This map has been created for Counter-Strike source.

Name: chaos_underground
Author: Oloil (www.fpsbanana.com)
E-mail: tom_samourai@hotmail.com

----------------------------------------------------

Notes: 

Be sure to allow the flashlight for this map, otherwise 
you will be totally blind. You should also active footstep
to make a more challengeful game. Finally, do not play with
bot, they doesn't seen to be affected by the darkness.

----------------------------------------------------

Law:

I allow everyone to edit chaos_underground without asking, but
be sure to mention my name. Also, this map and all his edited
version should be only downloadable on www.fpsbanana.com

----------------------------------------------------

Enjoy!
